By using the Egosta Devlogs app ("the app"), you agree to the following terms and conditions:

1. Account Creation and Use
The app allows users to create an account using any email address and password.

Email addresses can be random or manually entered

No email verification is required

This information is stored securely using Firebase Authentication

Google Sign-In is currently disabled

2. Data Privacy
We respect your privacy. The app:

Stores only the email address and password in Firebase for login/account purposes

Does not verify or use the email for communication

Does not collect or share personal information

Does not upload any media or video content

Please refer to our full Privacy Policy for more details.

3. Video Playback
Egosta Devlogs plays videos stored locally on your device.

No video files are uploaded or shared

You are responsible for the content you access or play

