You are responsible for ensuring that video content used with the app complies with applicable copyright and content laws.

6. Security
Your login details (email & password) are stored securely via Firebase Authentication.

We do not store passwords outside Firebase

No additional personal or sensitive data is collected

7. Disclaimer
The app is provided "as is." We are not liable for:

Technical glitches

Video playback issues

